#  Quick NSE Cheat Sheet (for your mental RAM)

### Default enumeration

`nmap <target> -sC -sV`

### Run vuln checks

`nmap <target> --script vuln`

### Script categories

`nmap <target> --script <category>`

### Specific scripts

`nmap <target> --script banner,http-enum,vulners`

### Aggressive mode

`nmap -A <target>`

